{"tid":1588571,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"機場打狗救人義士 係咪變condom?","createTime":"2019-09-23T01:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T12:37:39.000Z","uid":247840,"like":42,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"2272b6210cf7e054031033416da1d232d1e7bc91","tid":1588571,"uid":247840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:22:42.000Z","msg":"［3］ #提堂 #申請保釋<br />\n時間： 12:00 noon<br />\n地址：高等法院 第7庭 字樓<br />\n法官：彭寶琴<br />\n被告：葉XX<br />\n情況：還押‼‼(17/9)<br />\n控罪：一項暴動罪及一項對他人身體加以嚴重傷害<br />\n事件：#813機場<br />\n備注：對男子(黃耀華)的身體加以傷害，黃是當日拔槍的警員。警方事後並在被告住所搜到一系列示威者常用的工具，包括防毒面罩及雷射電筒、丫叉、彈珠等。控方指，案中警員黃耀華事後陰囊紅腫，手腳擦傷。<br />\n<br />\n==========<br />\n由【被捕人仕關注組 @youarenotalonehk】整理<br />\n本頻公告: <a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/144\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk%2F144&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=71694808\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/144</a><br />\n旁聽須知: <a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/296\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk%2F296&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=3252ac63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/296</a><br />\n<br />\n特別嗚謝交通資訊由【抗爭行動交通頻道 @ncetransport】提供<br />\n高等法院<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ncetransport/2457\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fncetransport%2F2457&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=4a790203\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ncetransport/2457</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>唔該大家，今次係革命<br />\n<br />\n哩位義士係英雄 係典範<br />\n<br />\n邊撚個再係度指指點點，唔可以乜乜乜哥D人<br />\n<br />\n唔撚該番屋企瞓教<br />\n<br />\n而家係革命，唔係去玩<br />\n<br />\n又話商場唔搞得，又要100個條件先可以私了<br />\n<br />\n道德潔癖撚番番去2014年啦<br />\n<br />\n而家2019架啦！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"7a313843e80c